&lt;li&gt;4 to 8 years of direct experience managing development programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Jira, Smartsheet, or other program management software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience engaging both internal engineering teams and external suppliers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent organizational, communication, presentation, and data analytics skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to focus on details and a resourcefulness to drive issues until they are resolved.&lt;/li&gt;
